<li id="cite_note-Ahlstrom2004-21"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Ahlstrom2004_21-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFAhlstrom2004" class="citation book cs1">Ahlstrom, Sydney E. (2004). <i>A Religious History of the American People</i>. Yale University Press. p.&#160;985. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780300100129" title="Special:BookSources/9780300100129"><bdi>9780300100129</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=A+Religious+History+of+the+American+People&amp;rft.pages=985&amp;rft.pub=Yale+University+Press&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft.isbn=9780300100129&amp;rft.aulast=Ahlstrom&amp;rft.aufirst=Sydney+E.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AChristian+Flag" class="Z3988"></span></span>
